  The Menu bar
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~
    o  You have likely noticed the numerous buttons at the top of the
       screen.  Here is an explanation of each:

    o  Contents:

          -  This returns you to the local table of contents.

          -  Each time you press it, you will go `up a level', and
             will soon be at the main Contents page, at the front of
             the book.

